QuestData.Title: Flying Colors
QuestData.Description: Well, I've done all that I can with you. Sounds like the others have, too.$b$bHigh Elder Cloudfall will be waiting at the banquet grounds, ready to celebrate your departure. Not that we're happy you're leaving... he just enjoys celebrations.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to High Elder Cloudfall at the Banquet Grounds in the Jade Forest.
